Prayer
2026-04-19

{Verse 1}
Turn my heart
Mould my soul
Not just part
But my whole

{Verse 2}
Cleanse my ear
Win my will
Quell my fear
Make me still

{Verse 3}
Soothe my mind
So I hear
Help me find
You in prayer

{Verse 4}
Save You draw
I can't seek
You make sure
We will meet

{Verse 5}
You invite
Summon me
Into light
And I'll see

{Verse 6}
In this place
Here You show
What to face
How to go

{Verse 7}
Bathed in light
'Fore Your throne
I delight
I am home


